author: USA TODAY, Sara M Moniuszko, USA TODAY
title: Prince Albert of Monaco denies passing the coronavirus to Prince Charles
description: Prince Albert, who tested positive for the coronavirus last week, is denying responsibility for Prince Charles positive test earlier this week.
content:
Prince Charles has tested positive for the coronavirus after displaying "mild symptoms," according to a statement.
